} 4 actor-spawn-capacity def    % capacity 4: forces backpressure

0 1 19 { bp-actor actor-send } for   % 20 messages into capacity-4
yield-many
bp-count 20 eq
    (backpressure: 20 msgs through cap-4 mailbox) rt-ok clear

